query: SELECT p.id, c.name as country, s.name as service, p.smshub_price, p.our_price, p.api_id FROM prices p JOIN countries c ON p.country_id = c.id JOIN services s ON p.service_id = s.id WHERE p.api_id = 3 LIMIT 10
